parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transfer Switch Failure and Electrical Fires
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transfer switch can cause electrical fires, which can lead to property damage, personal injury, or even death.
symptoms: Warning lights in the main fuse panel indicating a blown fuse
electrical fires in the storage compartment
smell of electrical fire
risk of fire
personal injury
and property damage.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Lack of Standard Wiring and Piping Diagrams
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The absence of standard wiring and piping diagrams makes it difficult to troubleshoot and repair issues, leading to prolonged downtime and increased costs for the owner.
symptoms: Difficulty in diagnosing and repairing issues
lack of standard wiring and piping diagrams
increased costs for repairs
and dealer reluctance to service the unit.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Poor Dealer Service and Warranty Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of cooperation from dealers and inconsistent warranty policies can lead to frustration and financial burdens for the owner.
symptoms: Dealer reluctance to service the unit
inconsistent warranty policies
extended warranties not honored by all dealers
and attitude of "if you didn't buy it here
I don't want your problems."

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fresh water tank supports can cause the tank to fall down while traveling, potentially leading to accidents, damage to the tank, and water leakage.
symptoms: The rear right side of the fresh water tank falls down while traveling
the metal U-channel supports under the tank bend down
the tap screws on each end break or pull through the frame
and the tank begins to drag on the road.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The improper installation of the toilet can cause sewage to be dumped into the gray water tank, leading to the rapid filling of the tank and the emission of raw sewage onto the ground while traveling.
symptoms: The toilet flushes into the gray water tank instead of the black water tank
the gray water tank fills up quickly
and raw sewage is emitted onto the ground while traveling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the detachable ladder brackets can cause the ladder to become unstable, potentially leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The plastic brackets that hold the steps to the ladder are broken or cracked
the ladder becomes unstable
and the steps may detach from the ladder while in use.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the D-Ring installation can cause damage to the trailer and its contents, and potentially lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: D-Ring pulls out of the floor
damage to trailer windows and contents
stripped screws
inadequate contact area between screws and aluminum flooring.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Floor Support Gusset Interference with Rear Tire
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The interference between the floor support gusset and the rear tire can cause tire damage or failure, leading to loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: Deformed metal from numerous contacts
potential tire failure
suspension compression issues.
